<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,883,965,991]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">
Key to the species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hoffman" authorityYear="2002" box="[412,591,965,991]" class="Insecta" family="Mantispidae" genus="Leptomantispa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
